Median Income by Census Tract, 2010 and 2015

A data set containing the estimated median incomes for each City of St. Louis Census Tract for 2010 and 2015.

data(stl_tbl_income)

Format

A tibble with 106 rows and 8 variables:

geoID

full census tract id number

tractCE

census tract id number

nameLSAD

census tract string

mi10

2010 median income estimate

mi10_moe

margin of error for 2010 median income estimate

mi10_inflate

2010 median income estimate in 2015 dollars

mi15

2015 median income estimate

mi15_moe

margin of error for 2015 median income estimate

Source

U.S. Census Bureau
